# CODEOWNERS — Orion Digital Solutions (.github)
#
# Defines required reviewers per path pattern. GitHub enforces these
# assignments automatically when branch protection rules are configured.
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern>  <@owner> [<@owner> ...]
# Patterns are evaluated top-to-bottom; the LAST matching rule wins.
# Use GitHub team slugs (@org/team) rather than individual usernames
# wherever possible so that membership changes require no edits here.
#
# Teams referenced:
#   @orion-digital-solutions/devops           — CI/CD pipeline owners
#   @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads — governance & community health
#   @orion-digital-solutions/security         — security policy & tooling
#   @orion-digital-solutions/marketing        — public-facing org profile

# ── Default (catch-all) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Any file not matched by a more specific rule below requires review from
# engineering leads.
*                                               @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads

# ── Reusable CI/CD workflows ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Changes here propagate automatically to every project repository on their
# next run. Requires DevOps review to prevent regressions org-wide.
.github/workflows/                              @orion-digital-solutions/devops @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads

# ── Workflow starter templates ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Templates copied into project repos. Same risk surface as workflows/ above.
workflow-templates/                             @orion-digital-solutions/devops @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads

# ── Security policy ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Vulnerability disclosure process. Requires security team sign-off.
SECURITY.md                                     @orion-digital-solutions/security

# ── Community health & governance files ───────────────────────────────────
# Org-wide defaults served by GitHub to all repositories.
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                              @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads
CONTRIBUTING.md                                 @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads
SUPPORT.md                                      @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads
PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md                        @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads

# ── Issue templates ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ISSUE_TEMPLATE/                                 @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads

# ── Public org profile ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rendered on the orion-digital-solutions GitHub org landing page.
profile/                                        @orion-digital-solutions/marketing @orion-digital-solutions/engineering-leads
